    "“Wife, I am long accustomed to losing on his account. It is my way.“",
    "妙容は気付いている。私が劉邦に賭けていることを。そして、私はその賭けに勝つために、彼女を質に取られても良いと思っている。", "She knows. She knows I am betting on Liu Bang. And to win that bet, I would let her be taken hostage."),
  chooseStep("bg-house", [
    Choice {
