      labelEn: "Tell Miao Rong the truth about your gamble",
      hintJa: "妻はあなたの『共犯者』になる。後年、韓信を罠にかける時、彼女が手伝う",
      hintEn: "Your wife becomes your accomplice. Years later, when you trap Han Xin, she will help",
      dKarma: 3, dWife: 8, dWifeFear: 0,
      dTrust: 0, dMinXin: 0,
      dBu: 0, dZhi: 0, dMei: 0, dZheng: 3,
      setFlag: "miao_accomplice", gotoScene: "xiaohe_act1_end"
    },
    Choice {
      labelJa: "「お前は知らずに居ればよい」と黙る",
      labelEn: "“You're better off not knowing“ — stay silent",
      hintJa: "妻は守られる。だが、あなたは孤独な共犯者として一生を生きる",
      hintEn: "She is shielded. But you walk this path alone forever",
      dKarma: 1, dWife: 2, dWifeFear: 0,
      dTrust: 0, dMinXin: 0,
      dBu: 0, dZhi: 0, dMei: 0, dZheng: 2,
      setFlag: "miao_protected", gotoScene: "xiaohe_act1_end"
    }
  ])
]

def xiaoheAct1End := [
  narr("bg-pei", "数年後、秦が傾き、沛の役人衆は劉邦を担いで蜂起する。蕭何はその参謀となった。彼の名は、ここから歴史に刻まれていく――そして、彼が韓信を見出し、そして殺す日まで、二十年は無い。", "Years later, as Qin tilts toward collapse, the clerks of Pei raise Liu Bang as their leader. Xiao He becomes the lead strategist. From here his name enters history — and the day he will discover Han Xin, then kill him, is less than twenty years away."),
  endingStep("xiaohe_act1_clear")
]

-- 范増 Act 1 stub: 老人として項梁を訪ねる
def colorFanZeng := "#3a5a3a"

